data.description: Very nice, remodeled handicap accessible home with an open floor plan. Three spacious bedrooms with a remote primary bedroom. Nice living area with a cozy fireplace. Great covered patio with an oversized back yard. Close to hospital, doctors, fire station, shopping, dinning and interstate. This home will not last long. Schedule to see today!
